snippet.title: Palworld - Gameplay Trailer | TGS 2023
snippet.description:
Palworld is coming to Xbox and Windows PC in 2024, and the latest TGS trailer shows off in-engine gameplay of combat, base building, Pal abilities, and faction leaders.
